---
title: Smart Shawarma Spiced Chicken Patties with Spinach Salad and Couscous
description: Chicken patties are mixed with big flavour makers like shallots and Shawarma Spice Blend before being pan-fried to juicy perfection in this recipe. Aromatic couscous and a zingy garlic sauce ensure you don't sacrifice taste for calorie and carb consciousness.
